### start game
POST http://localhost:3003/game-engine/start HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": "test-match-123",
    "players": [
        {"id": "player1", "username": "alice"},
        {"id": "player2", "username": "bob"}
    ],
    "mode": "local",
    "status": "waiting"
}

### right padde down
POST http://localhost:3003/game-engine/input/test-match-123 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": "test-match-123",
    "keyType": "press",
    "key": "l"
}

### right paddle up
POST http://localhost:3003/game-engine/input/test-match-123 HTTP/1.1
